Serbia Plans to Boost Irrigation to Aid Farming, Politika Says

-- B y   M i s h a   S a v i c
-- 
2011-07-11T08:07:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/serbia-plans-to-boost-irrigation-to-aid-farming-politika-says.html
Serbia will expand irrigation to
about a quarter of its 4.2 million hectares of arable land from
100,000 hectares at present,  Politika  newspaper reported, citing
Agriculture Minister Dusan Petrovic.  Plans for the project may be prepared by September and are
vital for increasing  food production , the report quoted Petrovic
as saying.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Misha Savic in Belgrade at 
 msavic2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at   jagomez@bloomberg.net  